title: Call Recording (City Of Palm Beach Gardens)

communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Florida Sunshine Law, I hereby request the following records:

Hello I would like to request the phone call recording on the night/evening of 1/23/2024 between Dispatcher Jess/Jessica/Jessy and Mason Turner and or phone number 561-320-7690. it should be a single recording and only call.
Please let me know if you have trouble finding this call recording.

If redactions are made, please provide the state statute pertaining to the redaction as required by state law.

Also please provide a direct download link for the information or reply to this email with the information attachment, as we have had issues using download links in the past please send the link to turnermason@gmail.com or attached in a zip folder if it is small enough.

There should be no fees associated with this request. I would ask that this request be filled via email attachment per Florida Sunshine Law.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 10 business days.

Sincerely,

Mason C. Turner

communications.subject: Texas Public Information Act Request: Migrants Bussed by TDEM
communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Texas Public Information Act, I hereby request the following records:

The exact number of migrants bussed out of state by the TDEM since 04/01/2023.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 10 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Kevin Ozebek

communications.subject: Texas Public Information Act Request: Exact Migrants Flown
communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Texas Public Information Act, I hereby request the following records:

The exact number of migrants flown out of state by the TDEM since 01/01/2023, broken down by flight.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 10 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Kevin Ozebek
